Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:08.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,小心火燭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要對炸豬排保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保密什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是炸豬排的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想制做特製涼拌豆腐和大家一起慶祝它的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:35.98,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,想見你  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說要回去什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續悠閒地待著就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說悠閒待著沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以給我悠閒點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  那傢伙…今天生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  可以去看一下豆腐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼無論怎麼做都會壓癟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因為太大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  還想做個大的給炸豬排一個驚喜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 要放棄還早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:03:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我也想些辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  行人都那麼說的話我再試一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人  媽媽紅豆大福做太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分送給你們一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  真是大饞鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊是小鈴的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以全部都吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了小鈴特別準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是把你的那份紅豆餡換成了激辣大福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:39.81,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,想像畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼  好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水  水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我和行人大人像紅豆大福一樣一起度過甜蜜的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不能吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不想吃也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實想吃到喉嚨都塞不進去的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在這涼拌豆腐完成之前  我會忍耐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福不是一秒就能吃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真頑固  那樣的話就讓我來你吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  吃吧  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說味道還不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是行人大人留在外面世界的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種年齡的健全男生擁有一個兩個戀人也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交往的兩人互定終身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是男人離家出走遭遇海難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流到孤島在那與絕世美女相遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有喜歡的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在如此美麗的你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無法偽裝自己的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  萬萬不可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你有喜歡的人  怎麼可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是罪孽多麼深重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被禁錮的戀 無用的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人激情燃燒的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話就不能呆在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個眼神不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在想念戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你以前有沒有看到過那麼悲傷的行人大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就讓他盡情沉浸在對戀人的思念中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給生日會的邀請帖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  今天是炸豬排的生日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不過說起來你沒精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難免小鈴會失落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實行人大人有留在外面的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是小鈴望塵莫及的可愛的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過比起她還是我比較有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人為我著迷 無法抵禦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還不知道是不是戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解你不想承認的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你也看到了吧  那行人大人有所思的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種深陷其中的眼神  不會錯一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,思念戀人的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,燃燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  不能呆在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,準備  準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實差不多是對故鄉產生眷戀之情的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶都那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不單是思念戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,思念故鄉或者家人都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是思鄉病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽說男人在失落的時候能簡單地攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今日一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收下你的策略了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能讓你搶先
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到不同於平常的我的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人也是一 擊 必 殺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就讓你忘記外面的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  真是喜歡搶先立功的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啦  只不過去看一下行人大人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你不是打扮得漂漂亮亮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凜才是  那行李是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是精心準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全是凜擅長的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是怪異的裝扮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓行人放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得穿上讓他覺得舒心的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從很早以前就準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦  洋服的話我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音那洋服一百年前就過時了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.41,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,落後時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是最新的流行趨勢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃呢  化了妝變身成成熟女性了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何  美麗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的完美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人也會超高興…不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來行人也為我著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不是化妝  是妖怪妝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去海邊了 行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才女孩的照片沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要和雪乃在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  難道想離開小島嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明知道出海很危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又被大漩渦捲進去了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  你這笨蛋  笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼想回到那女孩的身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  只是想把這個放出去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  居然奪走我的作戰方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴你真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒這打算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來大家那是什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是褶邊還是絲質琉璃都太落後時代了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  那千影小姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有什麼搞錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說公子很失落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想來安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命所做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起來用雪乃的魅力來安慰你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我來治癒行人大人內心的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人  為忘掉故鄉的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最好開始新的戀情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公子  用我的料理打起精神來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃也給你熱情的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來讓你忘記那個戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由我來讓他忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  大家快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…我來把戀人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說戀人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都說什麼戀人  究竟在說誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人所持有照片中的那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照片是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是指
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnzhunyuan}美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnzhunyuan}原來叫美咲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnzhunyuan}不對  美咲是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼戀人  完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  是誰說的給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  為什麼行人大人會有憂傷的眼神呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  剛才開始就有什麼在咕嚕咕嚕地在燒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然知道鹽鹵的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.58,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（鹽鹵  在海中提取食鹽後剩下的溶液）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那「苦苦」是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是「苦苦」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是鹽鹵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用在讓豆腐凝固方面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我家爺爺崇尚武學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是那種自己做蕎麥面和豆腐生活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我邊看著海一直都在想為何小鈴無法做好豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忽然想起以前爺爺做過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在想要讓豆腐凝固的鹽鹵是否不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那憂傷的眼神是在想豆腐的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看起來是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  行人用認真的表情在沉思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:16:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我也想讓炸豬排的生日會成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣就快完成豆腐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家能一起幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnzhunyuan}桃和笹身一整天都和小豬排玩的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  我累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一會了 加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼著急的回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸豬排 吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡拉阿開們也一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好  稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸豬排生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家為了慶祝炸豬排的生日而聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人什麼時候來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不來幫忙只有在吃的時候出現還真是不吃虧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸豬排兩歲了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才兩根蠟燭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,許願時如果能把火吹滅的話願望就能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  請吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  我自己會吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這邊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,式神召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託  嫁不出去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:29.00,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}「好害羞  玩偶裝」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸豬排那麼高興太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  信呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnzhunyuan}今天是美咲的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,約好在生日那天要陪她去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無法實現約定  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想著至少把信寄出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  其實你想回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是炸豬排的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自從來到這個島上受到許多炸豬排的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能丟下那麼拼命的小鈴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼現在就把信寄出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生魚片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為小瓶的話應該能穿過大漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不行嗎  無論怎麼扔都會被沖回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不能說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.46,0:22:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  成功了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:22:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:22:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:22:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了小鈴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  小鈴
